589
00:39:01,240 --> 00:39:03,527
Thật vô lí. 

590
00:39:06,440 --> 00:39:08,044
Tadashi.

591
00:39:09,080 --> 00:39:10,206
Gì?

592
00:39:11,280 --> 00:39:12,850
Tadashi.

